Privacy Policy
Committed to keeping your personal information private
This Privacy Policy is created by imagengine pty limited abn abn 14 127 517 702 and distributed with ‘Tarbiyah Storytime’ app.
Last update: Friday 28 August, 2020.
General
The application "Tarbiyah Storytime" is a collection of books that have been lovingly designed with great attention to detail to introduce children to an ayah of the Qur’an. The books are easy to follow and a great way for kids to either follow along and listen to each story, or use as a way to learn to read.
Collection of information
All received information is used exclusively to improve the quality of the application ‘Tarbiyah Storytime’ and cannot be transferred to third parties.
We do not collect any personal information.
We may collect non-personally identifying information about your mobile device through usage of our app.
                This information includes device type and model, operating system version and anonymous device identifier.
                We use this information to improve the quality of our application.
Advertising
The "Tarbiyah Storytime" app is completely free of ads.
Children's privacy
We do not knowingly collect personally identifiable information from children under 13. If you are a parent or guardian and you are aware that your child has provided us with personal information, please contact us. If we discover that a child under 13 has provided us with personal information, we will delete such information from our servers immediately.
Changes
Imagengine pty limited may update this information from time to time. We recommend you periodically check this document to be aware of the changes.
Contact
For any questions related to the Privacy Policy, you can always contact us via email: sales@imagengine.com.au